channel.title: Cant get this client to work
channel.description:
when i load this client on my server ip : fallen-fatalityrsps.no-ip.biz it gives me the error_game_js5connect, but when i use it on local host or 127.0.0.1, It works. How can i fix this so it works on my ip so others can use the client instead of just me, and once i get this to work ima Jar it.
Please no learn to do it yourself, i havent messed with RSPS's for about 4-5 years so if u know a fix id appreciate it if u helped me, thanks.
